Translation.LocalName: 事件和任务必须仅包含类型为“数据输入”或“数据输出”的项目感知对象。

Translation.Name: Events must bear a stereotype to define what type of event it is.
Translation.LocalName: 事件必须具有构造型以定义其事件类型。

Translation.Name: Events must not be decomposed. They must not contain other objects.
Translation.LocalName: 事件不得分解。 不得包含其他对象。

Translation.Name: Events must not be specified as reusable.
Translation.LocalName: 事件不能指定为可重用。

Translation.Name: Flows must either specify a message format or have their message format set to <None>.
Translation.LocalName: 流必须指定消息格式或将其消息格式设置为 <无>。

Translation.Name: Flows must have both a source and a destination object.
Translation.LocalName: 流必须同时具有源和目标对象。

Translation.Name: Gateways must not have more than one default outgoing flow.
Translation.LocalName: 网关不能有多个缺省传出流。

Translation.Name: Gateways/decisions must have more than one output flow to represent a split (conditional branch) or more than one input flow to represent a merge.
Translation.LocalName: 网关/决策必须有多个输出流以表示拆分（条件分支），或者有多个输入流以表示合并。

Translation.Name: Initiating and return messages must share the same correlation property of the same correlation key.
Translation.LocalName: 启动消息和返回消息必须共享相同相关键的相同相关属性。

Translation.Name: Initiating and return messages with inconsistent correlation settings
Translation.LocalName: 相关设置不一致的启动和返回消息

Translation.Name: Initiating messages must be of stereotype "Message Flow".
Translation.LocalName: 启动消息的构造型必须为“消息流”。

Translation.Name: Interfaces must contain at least one operation.
Translation.LocalName: 接口必须至少包含一个操作。

Translation.Name: Item-aware elements of type Data Input are not permitted in intermediate catch events.
Translation.LocalName: 类型为“数据输入”的项目感知元素不允许出现在中间捕获事件中。

Translation.Name: Item-aware elements of type Data Input are not permitted in message start events.
Translation.LocalName: 类型为“数据输入”的项目感知元素不允许出现在消息开始事件中。

Translation.Name: Item-aware elements of type Data Output are not permitted in intermediate throw events.
Translation.LocalName: 类型为“数据输出”的项目感知元素不允许出现在中间抛出事件中。

Translation.Name: Item-aware elements of type Data Output are not permitted in message end events.
Translation.LocalName: 类型为“数据输出”的项目感知元素不允许出现在消息结束事件中。

Translation.Name: Manual tasks cannot be exported to a NetWeaver BPMN2 file.
Translation.LocalName: 手动任务无法导出到 NetWeaver BPMN2 文件。

Translation.Name: Message flows can only go from (have as sources) activities, pools, throwing message intermediate events, or message end events.
Translation.LocalName: 消息流只能来自（将其作为源）活动、池、抛出消息中间事件或消息结束事件。

Translation.Name: Message flows can only point to (have as destinations) activities, pools, catching message intermediate events, or message start events.
Translation.LocalName: 消息流只能指向（将其作为目标）活动、池、捕获消息中间事件或消息开始事件。

Translation.Name: Message flows can only point to (have as destinations) activities, pools, catching message intermediate events, or message start events.
Translation.LocalName: 消息流只能指向（将其作为目标）活动、池、捕获消息中间事件或消息开始事件。

Translation.Name: Message flows must be connected to a maximum of one (not reusable) initiating and one return choreography task.
Translation.LocalName: 消息流必须至多连接到一个（不可重用）启动和一个返回设计任务。

Translation.Name: Message flows must specify a correlation property from among those defined in their correlation key.
Translation.LocalName: 消息流必须指定在其相关键中定义的相关属性。

Translation.Name: Message formats must not have the same definition as another message format.
Translation.LocalName: 消息格式的定义不能彼此相同。

Translation.Name: Missing input message (Request-Response)
Translation.LocalName: 缺少输入消息（请求响应）

Translation.Name: Missing input message (Solicit Response)
Translation.LocalName: 缺少输入消息（征求响应）

Translation.Name: Missing output message (Request-Response)
Translation.LocalName: 缺少输出消息（请求响应）

Translation.Name: Missing output message (Solicit Response)
Translation.LocalName: 缺少输出消息（征求响应）

Translation.Name: Multiple end events can only contain Message, Error, Escalation, Cancel, Compensation, Signal, and Terminate event definitions.
Translation.LocalName: 多重结束事件只能包含消息、错误、升级、取消、补偿、信号和终止事件定义。

Translation.Name: Multiple events must contain at least two event definitions.
Translation.LocalName: 多重事件必须至少包含两个事件定义。

Translation.Name: Multiple intermediate catching events can only contain Message, Timer, Conditional, Link, and Signal event definitions.
Translation.LocalName: 多重中间捕获事件只能包含消息、计时器、条件、链接和信号事件定义。

Translation.Name: Multiple intermediate throwing events can only contain Message, Escalation, Link, Compensation, and Signal event definitions.
Translation.LocalName: 多重中间抛出事件只能包含消息、升级、链接、补偿和信号事件定义。

Translation.Name: Not permitted in ad-hoc sub-process
Translation.LocalName: 不允许在即席子流程中

Translation.Name: Not permitted in event sub-process
Translation.LocalName: 不允许在事件子流程中

Translation.Name: Not permitted in intermediate catch events
Translation.LocalName: 不允许在中间捕获事件中

Translation.Name: Not permitted in intermediate throw events
Translation.LocalName: 不允许在中间抛出事件中

Translation.Name: Not permitted in message end events
Translation.LocalName: 不允许在消息结束事件中

Translation.Name: Not permitted in message start events
Translation.LocalName: 不允许在消息开始事件中

Translation.Name: Not permitted in tasks or events
Translation.LocalName: 不允许在任务或事件中

Translation.Name: Notification operations must specify an output message.
Translation.LocalName: 通知操作必须指定输出消息。

Translation.Name: Object names and codes must be unique for objects of the same type in the namespace.
Translation.LocalName: 对于命名空间中类型相同的对象，对象名和代码必须唯一。

Translation.Name: One-way operations must specify an input message.
Translation.LocalName: 单向操作必须指定输入消息。

Translation.Name: Parallel multiple intermediate catching events can only contain Message, Timer, Conditional, Link, and Signal event definitions.
Translation.LocalName: 并行多重中间捕获事件只能包含消息、计时器、条件、链接和信号事件定义。

Translation.Name: Request-response operations must specify both an input and an output message.
Translation.LocalName: 请求响应操作必须同时指定输入和输出消息。

Translation.Name: Resource flows must specify one or more CRUD (Create, Read, Update, or Delete) access modes to show how the resource will be used.
Translation.LocalName: 资源流必须指定一个或多个 CRUD（创建、读取、更新或删除）访问模式以显示资源的使用方式。

Translation.Name: Return messages must be of stereotype "Message Flow".
Translation.LocalName: 返回消息的构造型必须为“消息流”。

Translation.Name: Sequence flows must not have message formats attached to them.
Translation.LocalName: 顺序流不能附加消息格式。

Translation.Name: Service Provider name uniqueness
Translation.LocalName: 服务提供程序名称唯一性

Translation.Name: Service providers must contain at least one interface.
Translation.LocalName: 服务提供程序必须至少包含一个接口。

Translation.Name: Solicit response operations must specify both an input and an output message.
Translation.LocalName: 征求响应操作必须同时指定输入和输出消息。

Translation.Name: Start and end events are not permitted in ad-hoc sub-processes.
Translation.LocalName: 开始事件和结束事件不允许出现在即席子流程中。

Translation.Name: Start events of type Compensation are only permitted in event sub-processes.
Translation.LocalName: 类型为“补偿”的开始事件只允许出现在事件子流程中。

Translation.Name: Start events of type Error are only permitted in event sub-processes.
Translation.LocalName: 类型为“错误”的开始事件只允许出现在事件子流程中。

Translation.Name: Start events of type Escalation are only permitted in event sub-processes.
Translation.LocalName: 类型为“升级”的开始事件只允许出现在事件子流程中。

Translation.Name: Start events of type Standard are not permitted in event sub-processes.
Translation.LocalName: 类型为“标准”的开始事件不允许出现在事件子流程中。

Translation.Name: Start events that are not of type Standard are not permitted in sub-processes.
Translation.LocalName: 类型不是“标准”的开始事件不允许出现在子流程中。

Translation.Name: Starts must have at least one output flow.
Translation.LocalName: 开始必须至少有一个输出流。

Translation.Name: Sub-processes/composite processes must have at least one end.
Translation.LocalName: 子流程/复合流程必须至少有一个结束。

Translation.Name: Sub-processes/composite processes must have at least one start.
Translation.LocalName: 子流程/复合流程必须至少有一个开始。

Translation.Name: Tasks must not contain other objects. Only sub-processes and other composite activities can contain other objects.
Translation.LocalName: 任务不得包含其他对象。 只有子流程和其他复合活动可以包含其他对象。

Translation.Name: This check ensures that all properties have a stereotype "Correlation Property"
Translation.LocalName: 此检查确保所有属性均具有构造型“相关属性”

Translation.Name: Too few input or output flows
Unused correlation key in correlated conversation nodes
Translation.LocalName: 在相关会话节点中未使用相关键

Translation.Name: Unused correlation key in input correlated processes
Translation.LocalName: 在输入相关流程中未使用相关键

Translation.Name: Unused correlation key in output correlated processes
Translation.LocalName: 在输出相关流程中未使用相关键
